STATE of North Carolina
v.
Nijel Ramsey LEE-BEY. No. 416P15. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Dec. 15, 2015. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Nijel Ramsey Lee, for Lee, Nijel Ramsey. R. Andrew Murray, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 14th of December 2015 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Mecklenburg County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 15th of December 2015."
